== 足球以外 ==

愛華士是{{Link-en|絕對戒酒主義|Teetotalism|絕對戒酒主義者}}，他的性格非常內向，興趣只有釣魚、打撲克牌和去電影院<ref name="MN" /><ref name="book38">{{en}}McCartney, p38</ref><ref name="book61">{{en}}McCartney, p61</ref>。雖然，他曾經與隊友一同參加舞會，不過他在社交場合中卻缺乏自信<ref name="book39">{{en}}McCartney, p39</ref>。{{Link-en|占美·梅菲|Jimmy Murphy (footballer)}}形容他為「未被糟蹋的男孩」（unspoilt boy）並且保留著很重的[[黑郡|黑郡]]口音，因此他的隊友偶而會半開玩笑地模仿他的口音<ref name="Times">{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/sport/football/premier_league/manchester_united/article3285463.ece|title=Tragedy of the golden boy whose talent knew no bounds|work=The Times|first=Matt|last=Dickinson|accessdate=2008-02-13|date=2008-02-01|archive-date=2008-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081201060527/http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/sport/football/premier_league/manchester_united/article3285463.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>。有一次，他因為騎乘無燈的自行車而被警察攔下，並且遭當局和球會罰款5先令，以及兩星期的工資<ref name="bike">{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.sundaymirror.co.uk/sport/football/2008/02/10/dietmar-hamann-urges-man-city-fans-to-behave-for-minute-s-silence-98487-20314876/ |title=Dietmar Hamann urges Man City fans to behave for minute's silence |work=Daily Mirror |first=Simon |last=Mullock |accessdate=2008-02-14 |date=2008-02-10 }}{{dead link|date=六月 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }}</ref>。

愛華士逝世前居住在[[斯特雷特福德|斯特雷特福德]]金雀花大道的出租公寓<ref name="digs">{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_qn4158/is_20030407/ai_n12692153|title=FOOTBALL: Rooney's rise mirrored in simpler days of Edwards|work=The Independent|first=Graham|last=Kelly|accessdate=2008-02-22|date=2003-04-07|archive-date=2009-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090125203052/http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_qn4158/is_20030407/ai_n12692153|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他的未婚妻莫莉·利奇（Molly Leech）在[[奧爾特靈厄姆|奧爾特靈厄姆]]紡織機械製造商的辦公室工作，而爱德华兹去世时她年僅22歲。兩人在[[曼徹斯特機場|曼徹斯特機場]]一家酒店的宴會中遇上，交往一年後訂婚，他們亦是莫莉·利奇朋友約瑟芬·斯托特女兒的教父母<ref name="MN">{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.messengernewspapers.co.uk/news/munich/features/display.var.1985768.0.remembering_a_legend.php|title=Remembering a legend|work=Messenger Newspapers|first=Simon|last=Greenhalgh|accessdate=2008-02-13|date=2008-01-22|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20070726031310/http://www.messengernewspapers.co.uk/news/munich/features/display.var.1985768.0.remembering_a_legend.php|archivedate=2007-07-26}}</ref>。

愛華士亦曾在得力素[[葡萄糖|葡萄糖]]片劑的廣告中亮相，以及撰寫《防守球員這條路》（Tackle Soccer This Way）一書，由於這些商業活動，使他在球季期間每週獲得15英鎊的工資，夏天則是每週12英鎊<ref name="Times" />。他死後，他的家人批准將書出版，這本書停止出版多年後<ref name="SMN">{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.sundaymirror.co.uk/sport/football/2008/02/03/busby-babe-duncan-edwards-exclusive-98487-20308570/ |title=Busby Babe Duncan Edwards exclusive |work=Sunday Mirror |first=Rory |last=Smith |accessdate=2008-02-13 |date=2008-02-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080206090755/http://www.sundaymirror.co.uk/sport/football/2008/02/03/busby-babe-duncan-edwards-exclusive-98487-20308570/ |archivedate=2008-02-06}}</ref>，於2009年11月重新出版<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.tstw.co.uk|title=Tackle Soccer This Way|publisher=Kelmscott Press|accessdate=2009-11-19|archive-date=2010-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100626233521/http://www.tstw.co.uk/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

